  ('dcc59d55-be40-4c79-9120-b1efded75665','98eb2017-36d5-4d31-bcd2-37ff9e3c8ebb',86.0,'Owner age est ~66 (src: linkedin_grad), tenure 94yr (+4).',70.0,'Service mix=tax_bookkeeping (94yr recurring book).',90.0,'5 tells: No audit services (despite 90+ yr history); No advisory / CFO services; No client portal.',78.0,'Hot vertical (Citrin Cooperman/Aprio/Schellman/CBIZ TX expansion); tier-2 Galveston.',82.0,'A_acquire_self','94-yr Galveston CPA. Owner est ~66yr. Tells: 5. Eddie Walsh III UT 1982 CPA 1985 ~66; 4-gen family firm; was Galveston County Treasurer 2003-2023 (political career = winding down public acctg). A-tier candidate; deep-dive pending.','Move from compliance-only to advisory bundle (CFO/advisory/payroll), digital portal (Canopy/Liscio), 12-15% rate lift. Double EBITDA margin from ~25% to 40-45% over 24 months.','high',0.85),
